{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mm-mm, I'm not going to say thank you to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So there is still-- there's still unfinished business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There is unfinished business about not having a-- a cemetery to go to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There is unfinished business because I'm not able to portray my father to my children because it's difficult to talk to me-- talk about it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- for years-- I mean, there is in the literature the survival guilt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, for years I went around with the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thought, feeling, that if I wouldn't have existed, my father would have lived, because it was because I was a child that he had to leave.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Otherwise he could have stayed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it occurred to me only much later that I didn't ask to be born either.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, I mean, originally I focused on if I hadn't been around, my father would be alive now, and my mother would have a husband.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think everybody finds some way of finding an explanation for feeling guilty about surviving.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think that probably nobody, if you want to be totally [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bottom line about it, nobody who came back could come back without somebody else not going under.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Any transport that we stayed off of, somebody else went on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that-- that doesn't feel good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I-- it took a very personal tone with me with-- with the feelings that I had about my dad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't really-- I don't think I've ever been able to really talk to the kids about this period.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
